_sText:
BrokenSurf is alive and striving, I was originally going to call this map surf_argh, but decided against it because half the regulars that used to go to BrokenSurf don't go there anymore ever since the server swap (we didn't tell anyone).

This map isn't great, an experienced surfer could beat it easily, and it's sure as hell not one of Harvey's maps or anything, but I like it.
